uDD23\\uD83D\\uDE02\",\"author_id\":\"7820042\",\"created_at\":\"2021-03-07T03:42:30.000Z\",\"conversation_id\":\"1368406676265607171\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"in_reply_to_user_id\":\"7820042\",\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"id\":\"1368400831570092037\",\"source\":\"Twitter for iPhone\",\"public_metrics\":{\"retweet_count\":0,\"reply_count\":1,\"like_count\":0,\"quote_count\":0},\"text\":\"Did I mention that the hand-rail now becomes an new obstacle in the middle of an otherwise wide, open thoroughfare?\",\"author_id\":\"7820042\",\"created_at\":\"2021-03-07T03:19:16.000Z\",\"referenced_tweets\":[{\"type\":\"replied_to\",\"id\":\"1368398498215849986\"}],\"conversation_id\":\"1368397010332569604\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"entities\":{\"annotations\":[{\"start\":45,\"end\":46,\"probability\":0.3769,\"type\":\"Place\",\"normalized_text\":\"HK\"},{\"start\":150,\"end\":164,\"probability\":0.6376,\"type\":\"Place\",\"normalized_text\":\"Nam Fung Centre\"},{\"start\":170,\"end\":185,\"probability\":0.891,\"type\":\"Place\",\"normalized_text\":\"Tsuen Kam Centre\"}]},\"in_reply_to_user_id\":\"7820042\",\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"id\":\"1368398498215849986\",\"source\":\"Twitter for iPhone\",\"public_metrics\":{\"retweet_count\":0,\"reply_count\":1,\"like_count\":0,\"quote_count\":0},\"text\":\"It’s really unbelievable how hostile some of HK’s urban environments are to people with disabilities.\\n\\nThat was photographed at the bridge connecting Nam Fung Centre and Tsuen Kam Centre, not at some third-rate run-down mall.\",\"author_id\":\"7820042\",\"created_at\":\"2021-03-07T03:10:00.000Z\",\"referenced_tweets\":[{\"type\":\"replied_to\",\"id\":\"1368397010332569604\"}],\"conversation_id\":\"1368397010332569604\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"id\":\"1368397010332569604\",\"source\":\"Twitter for iPhone\",\"public_metrics\":{\"retweet_count\":0,\"reply_count\":1,\"like_count\":0,\"quote_count\":0},\"text\":\"Whoever decided to install this needs to be fired and sent back to school to learn accessibility.\\nWhat’s this? This is a hand rail for a *SINGLE* step. It serves absolutely ZERO purpose. Instead of installing a permanent ramp (there isn’t one yet), some idiot decided to waste $. https://t.co/tAj8F7Ecfk\",\"author_id\":\"7820042\",\"entities\":{\"urls\":[{\"start\":280,\"end\":303,\"url\":\"https://t.co/tAj8F7Ecfk\",\"expanded_url\":\"https://twitter.com/k_sze/status/1368397010332569604/photo/1\",\"display_url\":\"pic.twitter.com/tAj8F7Ecfk\"}]},\"created_at\":\"2021-03-07T03:04:05.000Z\",\"attachments\":{\"media_keys\":[\"3_1368397002975846408\"]},\"conversation_id\":\"1368397010332569604\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"entities\":{\"annotations\":[{\"start\":68,\"end\":78,\"probability\":0.5663,\"type\":\"Organization\",\"normalized_text\":\"Hacker News\"}],\"urls\":[{\"start\":0,\"end\":23,\"url\":\"https://t.co/AvjYlnwb12\",\"expanded_url\":\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=26366652\",\"display_url\":\"news.ycombinator.com/item?id=263666…\"}]},\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"id\":\"1368224733901156352\",\"source\":\"Twitter Web App\",\"public_metrics\":{\"retweet_count\":0,\"reply_count\":0,\"like_count\":1,\"quote_count\":0},\"text\":\"https://t.co/AvjYlnwb12\\nWhen you finally find like-minded people on Hacker News. hhhh \\uD83D\\uDE02\",\"author_id\":\"7820042\",\"created_at\":\"2021-03-06T15:39:31.000Z\",\"conversation_id\":\"1368224733901156352\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"id\":\"1368041836980269062\",\"source\":\"Twitter for iPhone\",\"public_metrics\":{\"retweet_count\":0,\"reply_count\":0,\"like_count\":0,\"quote_count\":0},\"text\":\"I can’t believe there is no Prêt à Manger around Tsuen Wan...\\n\\nhttps://t.co/UzDURxmzhw\",\"author_id\":\"7820042\",\"entities\":{\"urls\":[{\"start\":63,\"end\":86,\"url\":\"https://t.co/UzDURxmzhw\",\"expanded_url\":\"https://www.pret.hk/en-HK/find-a-pret\",\"display_url\":\"pret.hk/en-HK/find-a-p…\",\"status\":200,\"title\":\"Pret A Manger\",\"descripti