e damage has occurred without my Mail plug-in even being installed. Nevertheless, people contact me because it’s not unreasonable to wonder if third-party software is to blame,\",\"unwound_url\":\"https://mjtsai.com/blog/2019/10/11/mail-data-loss-in-macos-10-15/#comment-3393586\"}],\"mentions\":[{\"start\":24,\"end\":30,\"username\":\"Apple\",\"id\":\"380749300\"}]},\"created_at\":\"2021-02-04T00:46:40.000Z\",\"geo\":{\"place_id\":\"00dabde4090bf3b3\"},\"conversation_id\":\"1357128403690790914\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"entities\":{\"annotations\":[{\"start\":32,\"end\":36,\"probability\":0.5824,\"type\":\"Person\",\"normalized_text\":\"YYeTS\"}],\"mentions\":[{\"start\":0,\"end\":14,\"username\":\"DemogorgonPro\",\"id\":\"1226342462223814656\"}]},\"in_reply_to_user_id\":\"1226342462223814656\",\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"id\":\"1357013146620190721\",\"source\":\"Twitter for iPhone\",\"public_metrics\":{\"retweet_count\":0,\"reply_count\":1,\"like_count\":0,\"quote_count\":0},\"text\":\"@DemogorgonPro What exactly did YYeTS do though? Did they translate and release some movie that does not align with the official PRC ideology and narrative? I’m completely out of the loop?\",\"author_id\":\"7820042\",\"created_at\":\"2021-02-03T17:08:40.000Z\",\"referenced_tweets\":[{\"type\":\"replied_to\",\"id\":\"1357004256188854273\"}],\"geo\":{\"place_id\":\"0118e53a43a7db78\"},\"conversation_id\":\"1357003258280071168\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"entities\":{\"annotations\":[{\"start\":54,\"end\":58,\"probability\":0.3901,\"type\":\"Organization\",\"normalized_text\":\"YYeTs\"},{\"start\":97,\"end\":99,\"probability\":0.605,\"type\":\"Organization\",\"normalized_text\":\"PRC\"}]},\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"id\":\"1357003258280071168\",\"source\":\"Twitter Web App\",\"public_metrics\":{\"retweet_count\":0,\"reply_count\":1,\"like_count\":0,\"quote_count\":0},\"text\":\"Somebody fill me in about the deal with the arrest of YYeTs members? I mean, since when does the PRC police care abo